      <title>交易员重新考虑降息押注，债券 ETF 资金涌入创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/a-bond-etf-sees-record-influx-as-traders-rethink-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储今年大幅降息的希望逐渐减弱，投资者上周以有记录以来最快的速度涌入中期国债 ETF，并从短期债券上撤离。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/a-bond-etf-sees-record-influx-as-traders-rethink-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:20:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
